STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Jamar B. COCKREN, Defendant-Petitioner. C-538 September Term 2018
081522 Supreme Court of New Jersey. January 25, 2019

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001511-15 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is denied.
